# Gmail Configuration for Automatic Admin Notifications
# Follow these steps to set up automated email sending:

# 1. Create a Gmail account or use an existing one
# 2. Enable 2-Step Verification: https://myaccount.google.com/security
# 3. Generate an App Password: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
#    - Select "Mail" and "Windows Computer" (or your device)
#    - Copy the 16-character password generated
# 4. Set these variables:

GMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
GMAIL_PASSWORD=your-16-character-app-password

# Then rename this file to .env (remove .example)
# The server will automatically send form submissions to the admin email
